story.storyDescription: Lisa is just spending another night babysitting when all of the sudden she realizes she has no idea where the kids are...
story.title: Babysitting

messages.text: SOS!! My night has been a Blue’s Clues marathon since 6
at least you’re getting paid for babysitting the brats
hhmm I think 50 or 60...I don’t even know
when will you b free? maybe you can come later?
who else is at the party?
Petey, Rob, Mike, Michelle. UGH! She’s all over Sean!
hey brb gotta check on the kids
SERIOUS SOS!!! I can’t find the kids.
everywhere? what about cabinets or closets? the dryer?
It looks like a tornado hit the house...I’ve checked everywhere!!!!!
AND there’s a window open in the bathroom!!
Can a 6 and a 4 year old crawl out a window?
is there a screen on the window?
I’m in charge of someone else’s kids. =/
If I call the parents I won’t get paid. =/
And if I call my parents...I’m going to be grounded for life. =/
make sure you close that window
eeeewwwww Sean and Michelle are making out!
if I call the police, won’t they notify the parents?
Hhhmmm...kids missing, cops called? Alert parental units? Nah.
OF COURSE THEY’LL NOTIFY THE PARENTS.
I’m taking a flashlight and looking around outside.
if you were a kid where would you hide...or run away to?
their best friends live next door!
do you think I can spin this into an intense game of hide and seek for the neighbors?
I’m going to check the backyard.
cross your fingers they’re in the tree house and NOT in the pool
when was the last time you saw them?
the longer you wait...the harder it may be to find them
I’ll check inside one more time and then call
and there’s food all over the kitchen and cabinets are open
someone could have broken in and taken the kids after all!!!
you need to call the cops
what should I do until then????
think about where you last saw them
and make sure the door is closed
they were in this playroom watching TV
they looked like they were falling asleep
make sure you tell the cops everything
why couldn’t someone have stolen Michelle?
I can’t believe Sean is stupid enough to fall for her
if you don’t want to be alone...
uuuhhhh now I just want to disappear
I’m going to check inside the house again
check a room the kids aren’t allowed in
why would someone steal a laptop and food?
or some random room behind a dresser
lol where they bury the bodies
BUT IM SO GLAD THEY’RE ALIVE
I’ve never been so happy to see them
UH AND NOW THE COPS ARE HERE
at least it’s a funny story for your kids one day ;)
